room_title: Escape room "Escape Operation End of Days" by Mission Escape Games in Hartford
room_address: 76 LaSalle Rd, Unit 403 West Hartford, CT 06107
room_description: A top-secret mission has ended in failure and apocalypse is imminent. Humanity’s last hope rests with creating a special object known as the final element. You have managed to find the creator’s workshop with all the necessary materials, but the system will shut down in one hour! Do you have what it takes to complete Operation End of Days and save the world?
